snippet.title: 'Boxed In' PlayStation Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: 'Boxed In' will be released on PlayStation on May 28. Here's a look at two game modes. The first is: Survival, 4 colours, blocks from below. The second is Solitaire, 4 colours, blocks from back wall. The game can also be played in PSVR using the DUALSHOCK®4, the PlayStation® aim controller or two PlayStation® move controllers.
